{"kanda":6,"sarga":12,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"सतांपरिषदंकृत्स्नांसमीक्ष्यसमितिञ्जयः ।प्रचोदयामासतदाप्रहस्तंवाहिनीपतिम्","trans":"Then Ravana who is victorious in wars, looking at the vast assembly (of Rakshasas) ordered Prahastha, the chief of the army.","words":[{"d":"तदा:","m":"then"},{"d":"समितिञ्जयः","m":"one who is victorious in wars"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"कृत्स्नाम्","m":"vast"},{"d":"तांपरिषदम्","m":"that assembly"},{"d":"दृष्टवा:","m":"on seeing"},{"d":"तदा:","m":"then"},{"d":"वाहिनीपतिम्","m":"chief of the army"},{"d":"प्रहस्तम्","m":"to Prahastha"},{"d":"प्रचोदयामास:","m":"ordered."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"सेनापतेयथातेस्युःकृतविद्याश्चतुर्विधाः ।योधानगररक्षायांतथाव्यादेष्टुमर्हसि","trans":"\"O Chief of the army You order those who are well versed in the knowledge of all kinds of war and entrust those warriors of four divisions of the army to safeguard the city. Likewise, you ought to order them to be more alert.\"","words":[{"d":"सेनापते:","m":"O chief of the army चतुर्विधाः warriors of four divisions of army"},{"d":"कृतविद्याः","m":"those who are well versed in the knowledge of all kinds of wars"},{"d":"ते:","m":"you"},{"d":"योधाः","m":"war"},{"d":"नगररक्षायाम्","m":"to safeguarding the city"},{"d":"यथा:","m":"likewise"},{"d":"स्युः","m":"you entrust"},{"d":"तथा:","m":"so also"},{"d":"व्यादेष्टुम्","m":"you order to be more alert"},{"d":"अर्हसि:","m":"you ought."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सप्रहस्तःप्रणीतात्माचिकीर्षन् राजशासनम् ।विनिक्षिपद्बलंसर्वंबहिरन्तश्चमन्दिरे","trans":"Celebrated Prahastha desiring to carry out the king's order assigned the army inside and outside the city.","words":[{"d":"प्रणीतात्मा:","m":"celebrated"},{"d":"सःप्रहस्तः","m":"that Prahastha"},{"d":"राजशासनम्","m":"by king's order"},{"d":"चिकीर्षन्","m":"desiring to do"},{"d":"मन्दिरे:","m":"city"},{"d":"बहिः","m":"outside"},{"d":"अन्तश्च:","m":"inside"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"बलम्","m":"army"},{"d":"विनिक्षिपत्","m":"assigned."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"ततोविनिक्षिप्यबलंसर्वनग