ा:","m":"not think."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तनुमध्यापृथुश्रोणीशरदिन्दुनिभानना ।हेमबिम्बनिभासौम्यामायेवमयनिर्मिता","trans":"\"She is a woman of slender waist, plump hips, whose face is like an autumnal full moon. She is gentle and like a golden image. She is like a magical one constructed by Maya.\"","words":[{"d":"तनुमध्या:","m":"one of slender waist"},{"d":"पृथुश्रोणी:","m":"plump hips"},{"d":"शरदिन्दुनिभानना:","m":"of autumnal full moon like face"},{"d":"हेमबिम्बनिभा:","m":"like golden image"},{"d":"सौम्या:","m":"gentle lady"},{"d":"मयनिर्मिता:","m":"constructed by Maya (Rakshasa)"},{"d":"मायेव:","m":"like a magical one."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"सुलोहिततलौश्लक्ष् णौचरणौसुप्रतिष्ठितौ ।दृष्ट्वाताम्रनखौतस्यादीप्यतेमेशरीरजः","trans":"\"Beholding her smooth red soles and evenly shaped pinkish nails of feet, love is kindled in me.\"","words":[{"d":"सुलोहिततलौ:","m":"red coloured soles of feet"},{"d":"श्लक्ष् णौ:","m":"smooth"},{"d":"सुप्रतिष्ठितौ:","m":"evenly shaped"},{"d":"ताम्रनखौ:","m":"pinkish nails"},{"d":"तस्याः","m":"of her"},{"d":"चरणौ:","m":"feet"},{"d":"दृष्ट्वा:","m":"on beholding"},{"d":"मे:","m":"my"},{"d":"शरीरजः","m":"born in me"},{"d":"दीप्यते:","m":"kindled."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"हुताग्निरर्चिस्सङ्काशामेनांसौरीमिवप्रभाम् ।उन्नसंविमलंवल्गुविपुलांचारुलोचनम् पश्यंस्तदवशस्तस्याःकामस्यवशमेयिवान् ।","trans":"\"On beholding the sacrificial firelike face of Sita glowing like the radiance of the Sun, seeing her prominent nose, her large attractive countenance with beautiful eyes surely, I am overtaken by love and have become a slave to her.\"","words":[{"d":"हुताग्निरर्चिः","m":"like the sacrificial fire"},{"d":"सङ्काशाम्","m":"like the radiance"},{"d":"सौरीम्","m":"of Sun"},{"d":"प्रभामिव:","m":"like the glow"},{"d":"एनाम्","m":"her"},{"d":"उन्नसम्","m":"prominent nose"},{"d":"विपुलम्","m":"large"},{"d":"वल्गु:","m":"attractive"},{"d":"चारुलोचनम्","m":"beautiful eyes"},{"d":"तस्याः","m":"of her"},{"d":"तत्","m":"those"},{"d":"पश्यन्","m":"seeing"},{"d":"अवशः","m":"surely"},